@CryptoAlarmSystem.Api_HostAddress = http://localhost:5135
@userId = user123

### Health Check
GET {{CryptoAlarmSystem.Api_HostAddress}}/health
Accept: application/json

###

### Get Active Alarms (Default Pagination)
GET {{CryptoAlarmSystem.Api_HostAddress}}/api/v1/alarms/active
X-User-Id: {{userId}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Get Active Alarms (Custom Pagination)
GET {{CryptoAlarmSystem.Api_HostAddress}}/api/v1/alarms/active?pageNumber=1&pageSize=20
X-User-Id: {{userId}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Get Triggered Alarms (Default Pagination)
GET {{CryptoAlarmSystem.Api_HostAddress}}/api/v1/alarms/triggered
X-User-Id: {{userId}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Get Triggered Alarms (Page 2)
GET {{CryptoAlarmSystem.Api_HostAddress}}/api/v1/alarms/triggered?pageNumber=2&pageSize=10
X-User-Id: {{userId}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Get Alarm Logs (Default Pagination)
GET {{CryptoAlarmSystem.Api_HostAddress}}/api/v1/alarms/1/logs
X-User-Id: {{userId}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Get Alarm Logs (Custom Pagination)
GET {{CryptoAlarmSystem.Api_HostAddress}}/api/v1/alarms/1/logs?pageNumber=1&pageSize=50
X-User-Id: {{userId}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Get Crypto Symbols
GET {{CryptoAlarmSystem.Api_HostAddress}}/api/v1/alarms/crypto-symbols
Accept: application/json

###

### Get Notification Channels
GET {{CryptoAlarmSystem.Api_HostAddress}}/api/v1/alarms/notification-channels
Accept: application/json

###

### Get Alarm Types
GET {{CryptoAlarmSystem.Api_HostAddress}}/api/v1/alarms/alarm-types
Accept: application/json

###

### Create Alarm
POST {{CryptoAlarmSystem.Api_HostAddress}}/api/v1/alarms
X-User-Id: {{userId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "cryptoSymbolId": 1,
  "targetPrice": 50000.00,
  "alarmTypeId": 1,
  "notificationChannelIds": [1, 2]
}

###

### Update Alarm Channels
PATCH {{CryptoAlarmSystem.Api_HostAddress}}/api/v1/alarms/1/channels
X-User-Id: {{userId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "notificationChannelIds": [1, 3]
}

###

### Delete Alarm
DELETE {{CryptoAlarmSystem.Api_HostAddress}}/api/v1/alarms/1
X-User-Id: {{userId}}

###

### Update Price (Worker Service)
POST {{CryptoAlarmSystem.Api_HostAddress}}/api/v1/prices/update
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "cryptoSymbolId": 1,
  "price": 51000.00
}

###
